Package com.blockhaus2000.plugin

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IpmPlugin
    The main class that is used for plugin.
    IpmPluginClassLoader
    This class loader is used to provide class usage through plugins/jars.
    IpmPluginDescription
    The plugin description file that contains the main information of a IpmPlugin.
    IpmPluginLoader
    The plugin loader is used to load IpmPlugins.
    IpmPluginManager
    The plugin manager that manages all enable, disable, register and unregister logics.
    IpmServer
    The IpmServer provides some methods for the usage if the InternalPluginManager.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FakePlugin
    A fake Plugin that is used to "register" plugins in Bukkit.
    SimpleIpmPlugin
    An implmenetation of IpmPlugin.
    SimpleIpmPluginClassLoader
    This is a ClassLoader that extends the URLClassLoader to provide access to classes from other IpmPlugin's and access to the classses of the jar and the main classes (like CommandRegistrationUtil).
    SimpleIpmPluginDescription
    An implementation of IpmPluginDescription.
    SimpleIpmPluginLoader
    An implementation of IpmPluginLoader.
    SimpleIpmPluginManager
    An implementation if IpmPluginManager.
    SimpleIpmServer
    An implementation of IpmServer.
